"{\"uid\": \"rte.ie-news-world-2024-0903-1468101-uganda-olympian-icu\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"A Ugandan Olympian is in intensive care in a Kenyan hospital after being doused with petrol and set on fire allegedly by her partner, officials have said, in the latest horrific incident of gender-based violence in the east African country.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 240, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Long-distance runner Rebecca Cheptegei, 33, was assaulted after her Kenyan partner Dickson Ndiema Marangach reportedly snuck into her home in Endebess in the western county of Trans-Nzoia at around 2.00pm on Sunday while she and her children were at church, police said.\", \"from\": 242, \"to\": 512, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 263, \"end\": 270, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca_Napier\", \"score\": 0.9907860737749172, \"rank\": 0.009268037224383258, \"text\": \"Rebecca\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca_Napier\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca_Napier\"}, {\"begin\": 325, \"end\": 332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_Dickson\", \"score\": 0.7307567162224052, \"rank\": 0.3314482369772963, \"text\": \"Dickson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_Dickson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_Dickson\"}, {\"begin\": 384, \"end\": 392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Endebess\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Endebess\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Endebess\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Endebess\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Dickson, who had procured petrol, began pouring (it) on Rebecca before he set her ablaze,\\\" a police report said late yesterday, adding that he was also injured by the flames.\", \"from\": 514, \"to\": 689, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 515, \"end\": 522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_Dickson\", \"score\": 0.7307567162160914, \"rank\": 0.3314482369772963, \"text\": \"Dickson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_Dickson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_Dickson\"}, {\"begin\": 571, \"end\": 578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca_Napier\", \"score\": 0.9907860737749172, \"rank\": 0.009268037224383258, \"text\": \"Rebecca\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca_Napier\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca_Napier\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It said that neighbours had rescued the pair and taken them to nearby Kitale County Referral Hospital where they were admitted with \\\"multiple burns\\\".\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 840, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 761, \"end\": 767, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kitale\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kitale\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kitale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kitale\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They were transferred to Moi Teaching and Referral Hospital (MTRH), where Ms Cheptegei was admitted to the intensive care unit yesterday.\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 979, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 867, \"end\": 870, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_arap_Moi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.671656522051035e-27, \"text\": \"Moi\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_arap_Moi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_arap_Moi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Her condition looks serious with facial burns and bandages,\\\" a MTRH staff member said, requesting anonymity as they were not authorised to speak to the media.\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 1140, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The police report did not mention if Ms Cheptegei's children were hurt in the attack.\", \"from\": 1142, \"to\": 1227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Ugandan athlete and Mr Marangach were a couple who \\\"constantly had family wrangles\\\", the police report said.\", \"from\": 1229, \"to\": 1341, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1233, \"end\": 1240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\", \"score\": 0.9999999999979536, \"rank\": 2.109287930262937e-12, \"text\": \"Ugandan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Local media said the athlete had sustained burns over 75% of her body, and that her parents were travelling from Uganda to visit her.\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1476, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1456, \"end\": 1462, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.267436841772869e-20, \"text\": \"Uganda\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They said their daughter had bought land and built a house in the Trans-Nzoia area which lies on the border with Uganda, according to local media.\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1624, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1544, \"end\": 1555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trans-Nzoia_County\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Trans-Nzoia\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trans-Nzoia_County\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trans-Nzoia_County\"}, {\"begin\": 1591, \"end\": 1597, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.267436841772869e-20, \"text\": \"Uganda\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ms Cheptegei placed 44th in the marathon at the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1689, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Ugandan Athletics Federation expressed its regret over the incident, saying Ms Cheptegei had \\\"suffered severe injuries\\\".\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1815, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1695, \"end\": 1702, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\", \"score\": 0.9999999999979536, \"rank\": 2.109287930262937e-12, \"text\": \"Ugandan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This follows an incident involving her Kenyan boyfriend pouring petrol and setting fire on her,\\\" it said in a statement on X.  Gender-based violence in Kenya  A report by the Kenyan Bureau of National Statistics published in January 2023 found that 34% of women in Kenya have experienced physical violence since the age of 15.\", \"from\": 1817, \"to\": 2144, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1945, \"end\": 1966, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Domestic_violence\", \"score\": 0.999999997826535, \"rank\": 2.173572610826775e-09, \"text\": \"Gender-based violence\", \"types\": [\"Q12136\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Domestic_violence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Domestic_violence\"}, {\"begin\": 1970, \"end\": 1975, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.4538192018577964e-24, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\"}, {\"begin\": 2083, \"end\": 2088, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.4538192018577964e-24, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It said women who had \\\"been married are much more likely to have experienced violence\\\", noting that 41% of such women reported incidents compared to 20% of unmarried women.\", \"from\": 2146, \"to\": 2318, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The assault on Ms Cheptegei comes two years after Kenyan-born athlete Damaris Mutua was found dead in Iten, a world-famous running hub in the Rift Valley in the west of the country.\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2501, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2390, \"end\": 2397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Damaris_(biblical_figure)\", \"score\": 0.9999999689825931, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Damaris\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Damaris_(biblical_figure)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Damaris_(biblical_figure)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her death followed the murder of record-breaking runner Agnes Tirop, 25, who was found stabbed to death at her home in Iten in 2021.\", \"from\": 2503, \"to\": 2635, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2559, \"end\": 2570, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agnes_Tirop\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Agnes Tirop\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agnes_Tirop\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agnes_Tirop\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ms Tirop's estranged husband Emmanuel Ibrahim Rotich went on trial over her murder in 2023.\", \"from\": 2637, \"to\": 2728, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2666, \"end\": 2674, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Immanuel\", \"score\": 0.999997283217506, \"rank\": 1.4952408038297761e-06, \"text\": \"Emmanuel\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Immanuel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Immanuel\"}, {\"begin\": 2675, \"end\": 2682, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ibrahim_of_the_Ottoman_Empire\", \"score\": 0.5470962199307263, \"rank\": 0.8032551222215711, \"text\": \"Ibrahim\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ibrahim_of_the_Ottoman_Empire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ibrahim_of_the_Ottoman_Empire\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has denied the charges.\", \"from\": 2729, \"to\": 2755, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His trial is ongoing.\", \"from\": 2756, \"to\": 2777, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Source:AFP  \\u00a9 RT\\u00c9 2026.\", \"from\": 2779, \"to\": 2802, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"RT\\u00c9.ie is the website of Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann, Ireland's National Public Service Media.\", \"from\": 2803, \"to\": 2893, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2828, \"end\": 2851, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"score\": 0.9993664851270567, \"rank\": 0.0006339164685885233, \"text\": \"Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\"}, {\"begin\": 2853, \"end\": 2860, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999998023686398, \"rank\": 1.9763128778482032e-07, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"RT\\u00c9 is not responsible for the content of external internet sites.\", \"from\": 2894, \"to\": 2960, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2894, \"end\": 2897, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"score\": 0.9835396432123026, \"rank\": 0.013767790549921992, \"text\": \"RT\\u00c9\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Images Courtesy of Getty Images.\", \"from\": 2962, \"to\": 2994, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2981, \"end\": 2986, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"score\": 0.99368336328157, \"rank\": 0.006346665887163707, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\"}]}]}"